collectible.name: Lemosas
collectible.description:
This Lemosa puts a fun (and sour) twist on the classic mimosa with some homemade blueberry syrup, lemonade and champagne.

Editions: 77/77

Made by LaughAndBelly on 1st January 2022

--------------------------------------------

Ingredients:

- 1 cup sugar
- 1 cup water
- 2 cups blueberries
- Zest of a lemon
- 2 cups lemonade
- 1 bottle of champagne or Prosecco
- Fresh blueberries for garnish
